# <type>[(<scope>)][!]: <description>
# |<-----------  max 100 characters  ----------->|
#
# ---------- TYPE (required) ----------
#  feat      New feature
#  fix       Bug fix
#  refactor  Code restructure, no behavior change
#  style     Formatting only (no logic change)
#  docs      Documentation changes only
#  perf      Performance improvement
#  test      Tests added or corrected
#  build     Build system / dependency changes
#  ci        CI configuration changes
#  chore     Other changes (no src/test touch)
#
# ---------- SCOPE (optional, lowercase noun) ----------
#  Peripherals : uart | spi | i2c | adc | can | usb
#  Abstraction : hal | driver | bsp
#  Hardware    : gpio | timer | pwm | dma | watchdog
#  OS/RTOS     : rtos | scheduler | task
#  Boot        : bootloader | startup | linker
#  Memory      : memory | heap | stack
#  Tooling     : build | cmake | docs | ci
#
# Omit scope if change spans multiple unrelated areas.
#
# ---------- BODY (optional) ----------
# Separate from header with a blank line.
# Explain WHAT and WHY — not HOW.
# Max 100 chars per line.
#
#
# ---------- FOOTER (optional) ----------
#  Fixes #123
#  Related to #456
#  BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#
# Breaking change: add ! after type/scope
#   AND/OR add BREAKING CHANGE: in footer
#
# ---- DO NOT EDIT LINES BELOW ----
